She was doing long distance for majority of the relationship hence the word ablau was used to symbolise that miscommunication comes with distance but love is the end result.With time there became many uses of the word ablau. Ablau started being used as a question and became a short version of asking "do you love me?".The word with time also became popular for it's use as a nickname to refer to someone you love.
